. . "Now you must all be wondering who is this SethJi about whom all this is being said and written. 'SethJi is not a single person but a single force.... Any one can be a sethji. He maybe standing in a queue before you, he may be sitting next to you... or on the table opposite you in a restaurant... he may be doing a threadmill in your local GYM.... he may be swimming in the same pool as you.... he may be travelling in the same share auto... bus... train.....he may even be your local MLA or MP or... he may be your favourite hero or heroine......Or it may be SethJi itself who is writing this blog right now.....So guys and gals Just beware while you were doing all the above things you may have a great opportunity to meet the One and Only Legebrity [legend + celebrity] --- The Sethji... once you meet him you will be never able to forget him..."
.
